citeinfo.title: PublicSchools

descript.abstract: This schools dataset is composed of all Public elementary and secondary education in the United States as defined by the Common Core of Data, National Center for Education Statistics, US Department of Education. This includes all Kindergarten through 12th grade schools as tracked by the Common Core of Data. Included in this dataset are the military schools abroad and referenced in the city field with an APO or FPO address. Also referenced in the state field with the abbreviation AE. Please note that the APO and FPO schoolpoints are located at 0,0.

dataqual.logic: The National Center for Education Statistics (NCES) is mandated by Congress to provide complete statistics related to education in the US and other nations. Public school data are supplied by state education agency officials and includes fiscal and non fiscal related information. ORNL downloads the annual Common Core Data from the NCES website and geo-locates the public elementary and secondary schools on the appropriate building.
